<h1>Hotkey Buttons</h1>

<h2>Widgetised button</h2>

<p>Use <code>w-button</code> to create a <a href="/api/havok/widget/Button.html">havok/widget/Button</a>. A <code>w-button</code> can be used in place of any normal <code>button</code> tag.</p>

